This map contains a total of 8 levels:
- Deathrun
- Race
- Poolparty
- Team-Work
- Knife
- He
- Sniper (+ awps Scouts)
- Surf

Some Bugs are possible, but all the main parts have been fixed.
THX for report another bugs :)

Fixed version:
- some external textures were replaced to default valve textures
- bug in teamwork level is fixed
- sprites "glued" to BATTLEFORCE are erased; were visible through the walls and were useless
